{"tid":1229968,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【我咩都無講】大阪男子刀傷警員搶槍逃去　警員重傷昏迷","createTime":"2019-06-16T05:35:00.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-16T08:31:59.000Z","uid":46488,"like":2,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"67cdb77f8717eae0250e73904d220f295d6a5cc4","tid":1229968,"uid":46488,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T05:35:00.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/%E5%8D%B3%E6%99%82%E5%9C%8B%E9%9A%9B/341142/%E5%A4%A7%E9%98%AA%E7%99%BC%E7%94%9F%E8%A5%B2%E8%AD%A6%E6%A1%88-%E7%94%B7%E5%AD%90%E5%88%80%E5%82%B7%E8%AD%A6%E5%93%A1%E6%90%B6%E6%A7%8D%E9%80%83%E5%8E%BB-%E8%AD%A6%E5%93%A1%E9%87%8D%E5%82%B7%E6%98%8F%E8%BF%B7\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%25E5%258D%25B3%25E6%2599%2582%25E5%259C%258B%25E9%259A%259B%2F341142%2F%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E9%2598%25AA%25E7%2599%25BC%25E7%2594%259F%25E8%25A5%25B2%25E8%25AD%25A6%25E6%25A1%2588-%25E7%2594%25B7%25E5%25AD%2590%25E5%2588%2580%25E5%2582%25B7%25E8%25AD%25A6%25E5%2593%25A1%25E6%2590%25B6%25E6%25A7%258D%25E9%2580%2583%25E5%258E%25BB-%25E8%25AD%25A6%25E5%2593%25A1%25E9%2587%258D%25E5%2582%25B7%25E6%2598%258F%25E8%25BF%25B7&d=GKwB35BxKisFbiFxv4h%2Fhv7iMF%2BZ1QNuv%2BvReNsMrP0%3D&h=827944aa\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/%E5%8D%B3%E6%99%82%E5%9C%8B%E9%9A%9B/341142/%E5%A4%A7%E9%98%AA%E7%99%BC%E7%94%9F%E8%A5%B2%E8%AD%A6%E6%A1%88-%E7%94%B7%E5%AD%90%E5%88%80%E5%82%B7%E8%AD%A6%E5%93%A1%E6%90%B6%E6%A7%8D%E9%80%83%E5%8E%BB-%E8%AD%A6%E5%93%A1%E9%87%8D%E5%82%B7%E6%98%8F%E8%BF%B7</a><br />\n即時國際<br />\n撰文：歐敬洛<br />\n2019-06-16 12:07<br />\n最後更新日期：2019-06-16 12:07<br />\n<br />\n日本大阪發生襲警搶槍事件。事發於當地周日（16日）清晨約5時，大阪吹田市近千里山站，<strong>一名年約30歲的男子持刀襲擊一名駐守附近派出所警員，並搶槍逃走</strong>。被襲擊警員身受重傷，正於醫院搶救。<br />\n<br />\n日本放送協會（NHK）引述警方消息報道，該男子先在鄰近的關大前站，利用公眾電話報警指發現有人爆竊空屋，再前往千里山站襲擊派出所警員，奪槍逃去。<strong>被襲擊警員身上有多處刀傷</strong>，重傷昏迷，現正於醫院搶救。<br />\n<br />\n失竊警槍內確認有5顆子彈，警方懷疑行兇者有計劃犯案，企圖以報警引開派出所人員再施予襲擊，警方正全力追捕逃犯下落。<br />\n<br />\n此次是繼2018年9月一名大學生襲擊警局，刺殺一名警員並遭當場擊斃後，又一宗襲警事件。日本警方正強化保護警方安全措施，包括讓警員穿着難以遭刀刃直接刺傷的服裝，及增加派出所警員數量等。"},{"pid":"4e69816c8f9248fea09d7983ae6fa742c1f13461","tid":1229968,"uid":4618,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T05:51:34.000Z","msg":"g20之前搶槍<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"734d5837f93bd2b65e9f07db5bb09396ff752b29","tid":1229968,"uid":236404,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"4e69816c8f9248fea09d7983ae6fa742c1f13461","tid":1229968,"uid":4618,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T05:51:34.000Z","msg":"g20之前搶槍<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T06:03:51.000Z","msg":"山口矢二 ver2.0"},{"pid":"0954adf5c469fad468ecb1428341cd10dfa4f825","tid":1229968,"uid":46488,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"734d5837f93bd2b65e9f07db5bb09396ff752b29","tid":1229968,"uid":236404,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"4e69816c8f9248fea09d7983ae6fa742c1f13461","tid":1229968,"uid":4618,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T05:51:34.000Z","msg":"g20之前搶槍<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T06:03:51.000Z","msg":"山口矢二 ver2.0"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T06:06:17.000Z","msg":"日本人既愛國精神真係唔係香港可以比擬"},{"pid":"a9d32b339940ee797bb00ad3db1bc17d7a45fdb7","tid":1229968,"uid":4618,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T07:50:43.000Z","msg":"戒嚴了<br />\n<br />\n外出自粛や公共施設閉鎖&hellip;警官刺傷、大阪が厳戒態勢<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.asahi.com/sp/articles/ASM6J45W1M6JPTIL017.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.asahi.com%2Fsp%2Farticles%2FASM6J45W1M6JPTIL017.html&d=GKwB35BxKisFbiFxv4h%2Fhv7iMF%2BZ1QNuv%2BvReNsMrP0%3D&h=066e3cf1\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.asahi.com/sp/articles/ASM6J45W1M6JPTIL017.html</a>"},{"pid":"d69c2ddd29e620c7768618ea1eae8c74a5f7e6da","tid":1229968,"uid":46488,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pi